{"type":"text","timestamp":1780738312442,"sessionID":"ses_163bcc508ffey1OIiwa9Lcz6qq","part":{"id":"prt_e9c462bf5001ktU6i378azXlxF","messageID":"msg_e9c4620d1001Np54i4Id3LJzQR","sessionID":"ses_163bcc508ffey1OIiwa9Lcz6qq","type":"text","text":"The live feedback ledger is already shadow-only and write-safe by default, while the planned reducer children would add active consumers. That makes the `008` amendment a sequencing blocker: event capture can proceed, but active causal/retention consumers should be deferred or re-scoped before implementation.","time":{"start":1780738305013,"end":1780738312439},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d13bffc736b6061016a23e90100848191ad3f4954897e4a3a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
